sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:modificationsToBackbone: Primers carrying Picornavirus “self-cleaving” P2a sequence and cloning sites were synthesized and used for amplifying the DNA fragment carrying P2a-copGFP joint-coding sequence from plasmid PCDH-CMV-MCS-EF1-copGFP (System Biosciences). The fragment obtained was inserted into BamHI and XhoI sites in pSuper-puro vector. Two homology arms were amplified from GAPDH genomic locus, and inserted into MfeI and MluI sites at 5’ and HpaI and XhoI sites at 3’ of the 2a-copGFP fragment.
